    "improvements_made": "Added a dedicated RESULT entity to store official race outcomes (final rank, finish time, prize) and removed final_rank from RACE_HORSE, enabling clear separation of participation data and results. Made the JOCKEY relationship to RACE_HORSE optional (0:1) to reflect that jockey data may not be required for core betting. Included foreign keys that allow BET_DETAIL to be compared against RESULT for win/lose settlement. Retained the comprehensive STATISTICS entity for analytical reporting. Kept PAYMENT as a separate optional entity for flexibility, while preserving all strong points of the previous high‑scoring design."
